类 Entrant

java.lang.Object
com.example.cmput301project.model.User
com.example.cmput301project.model.Entrant
public class Entrant extends User
Represents an Entrant, extending the User class. An Entrant can join or leave events and has personal information such as name, email, phone, and profile picture URL.
作者:
Xinjia Fan
